releases.description:
- 优化 AI 设置；
- 优化 pdf 单词高亮；

---

- Optimize AI settings;
- Optimize PDF word highlighting;

- 增加短语识别功能 [#19](https://github.com/CatMuse/HiWords/issues/19)。🌰 栗子： 短语格式 `take ... into account` ，在文章中出现 `take all factors into account` 会正确匹配；
- 优化设置菜单单词本解析数据不准确问题；
- 支持韩语生词列表显示；

---

- Added phrase recognition function [#19](https://github.com/CatMuse/HiWords/issues/19). 🌰 Example: For the phrase format `take ... into account`, when `take all factors into account` appears in an article, it will be correctly matched;
- Optimized the issue of inaccurate data parsing in the settings menu wordbook;
- Supported displaying Korean new word lists;

